# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Legacy Microdent / FoxPro — do NOT commit real DATA or binaries
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Real clinic DATA, legacy install trees, and FoxPro/VB runtime files must never
# be committed to this repository. Use DATA_ROOT (or equivalent) pointing at a
# path outside git for read-only local testing against a copied DATA folder.
#
# The only DBF that belongs in git is the synthetic bridge test fixture below.

# If legacy folders are ever linked or copied under the repo root, keep them out of git:
/Microdent-Legacy/
/Microdent-Legacy-Copy/
/DATA/
/DATA old/
/DATA ORIG/

